data.description: This heavily upgraded, lakefront 5-bed, 4-bath, 3-car garage home with saltwater pool, integrated surround sound audio system, central vacuum, and a Generac whole home generator is a rare find in Martin County. Conveniently located to Interstate-95, the gated community of River Marina includes access to the community boat ramp, swimming pool, gym, and clubhouse. The main living space on the first floor offers 10' ceilings and crown molding throughout. All bedrooms are well positioned on the second floor with 9'4 ceilings. The primary bedroom offers a private balcony overlooking the lake and pool. The fourth bedroom offers a walk-in closet and private en-suite bath. Den/5th bedroom features double doors. Garage features epoxy floors, ceiling mounted storage racks and wall cabinets. Upgrades installed since 2022: impact glass windows and doors throughout, two A/C systems, freshly painted exterior, screened in patio and balcony, dual water heaters, dishwasher and garbage disposal.
